name: Slumber 1 by Zinus 8" Spring Mattress-In-a-Box
shortDescription: Sleep more comfortably at night with a convenient Slumber 1-8'' Mattress in a Box (Multiple Sizes). It is ready to use on platform beds and easy to set up for standard beds. The Slumber 1 Mattress in a Box features a firm and tightly wound top bed mattress with integrated individual spring coils that provide a customized feel that conforms to the shape of your body. The springs are spaced close enough to provide optimal support, yet far enough apart to increase motion separation and provide more undisturbed rest. The tight top mattress also features breakthrough rebound technology, meaning that the mattress is tightly packed when shipped to conserve space and naturally expands in just a few hours. Other bedding accessories, like foundations and bed frames, are available separately. Each Slumber 1-8'' Mattress in a Box (Multiple Sizes) comes complete with a 10-year limited warranty.

name: Apple iPad mini 2 16GB WiFi
shortDescription: Bigger screen than a smartphone; smaller and more convenient than a laptop — don't let the in-between size of this mini tablet fool you, because this powerful little device boasts some serious computing chops in a sleekly-designed package. The Apple iPad mini 2 offers a stunning 7.9" Retina display with over 3.1 million pixels, so photos and videos look incredibly detailed and text is razor sharp. The device features a powerful and power-efficient A7 chip with 64-bit architecture, so it's  remarkably responsive — while still delivering up to 10 hours of battery life on a single charge. The iPad mini 2 also offers ultrafast wireless, iSight and FaceTime HD cameras, and includes some awesome apps like iPhoto, iMovie, GarageBand, Pages, Numbers and Keynote.1 All this, and it still fits easily in one hand.Apple iPad mini 2 with Retina Display with Wi-Fi Space Gray or Silver:

name: Oakland Living Rose Patio Bistro Set
categoryPath: Patio & Garden/Patio Furniture/Shop Patio Furniture by Material/Metal Patio Furniture/Shop All Metal Patio Furniture
shortDescription: Bring style and functionality to your outdoor living space with the Rose 3-Piece Bistro Patio Set. It comes with a round table with two chairs in an elegant rose pattern. This attractive patio furniture bistro set has furniture legs made of sturdy cast iron. It offers a traditional style with an antique bronze finish and an aluminum table top. It is ideal for an intimate dinner for two or an afternoon cup of tea. This charming Rose 3-Piece Bistro Patio Set is suitable for placement in a garden, three-season room, on a patio or deck. A hole in the center of the table allows you to accessorize with an umbrella offering shade from the sun. It complements a wide range of outdoor decors. It is easy to assemble and each chair in this comfortable seating group has the capacity to support up to 200 lbs.
longDescription: <p> </p>Oakland Living Specializing in the creation of top-notch cast aluminum, iron, resin wicker, and stone outdoor furniture and accents, Oakland Living has been in the outdoor-furniture manufacturing business for over 15 years. From garden stones to complete furniture sets, they're renowned for their ability to provide their customers with high-quality pieces at a great price. A 72,000-square-foot distribution center, located in Rochester, MI, houses a supply of their best sellers, making it easy and convenient to ship items quickly to customers across the nation.

name: Abu Garcia Black Max Reel
categoryPath: Sports & Outdoors/Outdoor Sports/Fishing/Fishing Reels/All Fishing Reels
shortDescription: The Abu Garcia Black Max Reel is designed for anglers who require durability and dependability from a fishing reel. The Abu Garcia Max Reel features seven stainless-steel ball bearings and 1 roller bearing, a machine double-anodized aluminum spool and a Power Disk drag system that provides smooth drag performance. The Abu Garcia Reel's compact bent handle and star, accompanied by a recessed foot reel, provide a more ergonomic design. This Abu Garcia Black Max Reel is offered in black with red and silver accents that will complement almost any fishing rod. The Abu Garcia Reel is precision engineered to provide a smoother feel and increased performance on the water.
longDescription: Abu Garcia Black Max Reel:Precision engineered with a smoother feel and increased performance on the water7 stainless steel ball bearings and 1 roller bearing provide smooth operationMachined double-anodized aluminum spool provides strength without adding excess weightPower Disk drag system gives smooth drag performanceCompact bent handle and star provide a more ergonomic designRecessed reel foot allows for a more ergonomic reel design1-piece graphite frameGraphite side platesColor: black with red and silver accents

name: Ozark Trail 2-Room Instant Shower/Utility Shelter
categoryPath: Sports & Outdoors/Outdoor Sports/Camping Gear/Shop Camping Brands/Ozark Trail/Ozark Trail Tents
shortDescription: Why rough it? The Ozark Trail Instant Shower/Utility Shelter is the perfect way to enjoy the outdoors in comfort. It sets up in just seconds thanks to the innovative pre-attached instant frame design. The five-gallon solar shower is also included and heats up in just minutes from the sun. The shower includes a separate changing/utility room so your clothes stay dry and secure. Best of all, the walls are coated with a silver aluminum for complete privacy.
